query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-styles',
'fopen',
'hibernate-criteria',
'http-status-code-403',
'hybrid-mobile-app',
'intervals',
'macos-sierra',
'monogame',
'sendgrid',
'shuffle',
'stdvector',
'swap',
'template-engine',
'winscp');
